 *
 * THE SUBSUMPTION (the proof the name dissolves): over all 36 value-pairs,
 *     assim_meet       == l6_and   (the universal conjunction IS the named AND)
 *     assim_join       == l6_or    (the universal disjunction IS the named OR)
 *     assim_complement == l6_not   (the universal involution IS the named NOT)
 * If all three hold, the named primitive is PROVABLY a geometric fold (ml_named_is_redundant) -- the
 * sovereign gate that licenses its deprecation.  The mechanism is general: any lattice-structured named
 * primitive is shattered and subsumed the same way (the "also all others" horizon).
